{"tid":1238996,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［暴動］ 一係全部無罪 一係告晒所有人！","createTime":"2019-06-18T04:21:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T10:41:22.000Z","uid":154585,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1d140097148e6014f2c10684b43938c3a093eb5e","tid":1238996,"uid":154585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:21:49.000Z","msg":"根據公安條例第19條 &ldquo;暴動&rdquo; 定義<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;如任何參與憑藉第18(1)條被定為非法集結的集結的人破壞社會安寧，該集結即屬暴動，而集結的人即屬集結暴動。  (由1970年第31號第12條修訂)&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap245\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap245&d=7EcP4%2BvGpl6inSsjOqiUXnjBGfL1Jh2LWroBhk3D7pk%3D&h=250d59e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap245</a><br />\n<br />\n根據定義，首先今次唔係非法集結，而係有不反對通知書嘅合法示威，已經冇可能成立暴動<br />\n第二冇可能按警方講法只會有個別人士符合暴動罪而其他有份參與人士冇事<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以警方明顯無理拘捕，必須立即釋放所有被捕人士！</span></span>"},{"pid":"3f21525e2a7dafb9226ae8954f14cd207ea85081","tid":1238996,"uid":154585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:23:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0e05d3637fa8cab34ae00decf26a5e1c277816f6","tid":1238996,"uid":154585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:25:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"65e62b23a9974f2495c568960f0c2d3c2a90df98","tid":1238996,"uid":71799,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:28:27.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n唔可以比義士有事<br />\n一係就拉撚晒我地<br />\n坐爆監獄"},{"pid":"b1f8f86d468546e1813c2ea1c70dd5bfc08977df","tid":1238996,"uid":38237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:31:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"30307eefb9b9a1e04db7a1113c21bfcbe750de48","tid":1238996,"uid":154585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:34:28.000Z","msg":"救義士！救義士！"},{"pid":"cd36e7ec9d6928bbc053bce734c778f3389be543","tid":1238996,"uid":154585,"like":